00:28:35.920 --> 00:28:39.230 align:middle line:84%
And it's not just
about the frequency.

00:28:39.230 --> 00:28:41.150 align:middle line:84%
It's not just about
the intention.

00:28:41.150 --> 00:28:44.210 align:middle line:84%
It's not just about the emotion
or just about the harmonics.

00:28:44.210 --> 00:28:46.100 align:middle line:90%
It's about all of them together.

00:28:46.100 --> 00:28:48.350 align:middle line:10%
So my intention when
I created a Heart Code

00:28:48.350 --> 00:28:51.920 align:middle line:10%
was about bringing people
to a sacred place, where

00:28:51.920 --> 00:28:56.150 align:middle line:10%
they can discover and
listen to their own hearts.

00:28:56.150 --> 00:28:58.670 align:middle line:84%
So before I moved
into that process,

00:28:58.670 --> 00:29:02.610 align:middle line:84%
I always had to be emotionally
aligned with that intention,

00:29:02.610 --> 00:29:06.120 align:middle line:84%
because you can have an
intention, but if I walk in

00:29:06.120 --> 00:29:08.790 align:middle line:84%
and I'm in an angry
state, that's going

00:29:08.790 --> 00:29:11.140 align:middle line:90%
to go into the music as well.

00:29:11.140 --> 00:29:13.430 align:middle line:84%
So I would have to move
to that reverent state

00:29:13.430 --> 00:29:15.730 align:middle line:84%
that you're talking
about beforehand.

00:29:15.730 --> 00:29:19.310 align:middle line:84%
And in the Heart
Codes, that is created.

00:29:19.310 --> 00:29:22.860 align:middle line:84%
I would not be
creating in that space

00:29:22.860 --> 00:29:26.050 align:middle line:84%
if I was in a mood that was
out of context with that.

00:29:26.050 --> 00:29:29.160 align:middle line:84%
So that is what you're
feeling within that reverence.

00:29:29.160 --> 00:29:31.760 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's where
music is going now.

00:29:31.760 --> 00:29:34.750 align:middle line:84%
We're calling it designer music,
being able to design and put

00:29:34.750 --> 00:29:36.810 align:middle line:84%
specific emotions
and music, because we

00:29:36.810 --> 00:29:39.670 align:middle line:90%
know it carries a field.

00:29:39.670 --> 00:29:44.700 align:middle line:84%
And so this, again, is
composed at 60 beats per minute

00:29:44.700 --> 00:29:47.400 align:middle line:84%
