not just for our emotions.

00:29:54.980 --> 00:29:59.300 align:middle line:84%
But we know, we've studied
that these emotions bring us

00:29:59.300 --> 00:30:02.920 align:middle line:84%
into a state that's coherent
and also affect our heart

00:30:02.920 --> 00:30:06.660 align:middle line:84%
rate variability, which is
our measurement of our heart

00:30:06.660 --> 00:30:07.460 align:middle line:90%
health.

00:30:07.460 --> 00:30:08.260 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: Right.

00:30:08.260 --> 00:30:12.000 align:middle line:84%
GOLDSTEIN: And also works with
bringing our immune functions

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:15.430 align:middle line:84%
up and bettering it,
our cognitive abilities,

00:30:15.430 --> 00:30:17.140 align:middle line:84%
and also dealing
with environmental

00:30:17.140 --> 00:30:19.760 align:middle line:84%
stresses and
stresses that go on.

00:30:19.760 --> 00:30:23.550 align:middle line:84%
So that was really geared
towards the emotional body

00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:28.330 align:middle line:84%
affecting the physical body,
clearing the mental body,

00:30:28.330 --> 00:30:31.130 align:middle line:84%
and then having a deepening
connection in the spiritual.

00:30:31.130 --> 00:30:31.930 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: Yes.

