00:32:45.740 --> 00:32:47.120 align:middle line:90%
Like you immediately go there.

00:32:47.120 --> 00:32:47.450 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: Oh, yeah.

00:32:47.450 --> 00:32:48.250 align:middle line:90%
GOLDSTEIN: Right?

