anxiety attacks.

00:33:15.550 --> 00:33:18.574 align:middle line:84%
What music would
you suggest for me?

00:33:18.574 --> 00:33:20.490 align:middle line:84%
And I think she thought
I was going to suggest

00:33:20.490 --> 00:33:22.320 align:middle line:90%
like meditational music.

00:33:22.320 --> 00:33:25.360 align:middle line:84%
But in this specific
case, I asked

00:33:25.360 --> 00:33:27.730 align:middle line:90%
