00:33:27.730 --> 00:33:29.910 align:middle line:84%
What song, when
you listen to it,

00:33:29.910 --> 00:33:32.980 align:middle line:84%
you have a hard time being
in a state of anxiety?

00:33:32.980 --> 00:33:35.300 align:middle line:84%
And even before
she said it, I can

00:33:35.300 --> 00:33:39.060 align:middle line:84%
see her moving out of
anxiety and asking me.

00:33:39.060 --> 00:33:40.670 align:middle line:90%
