00:33:40.670 --> 00:33:41.470 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: Oh, god.

00:33:41.470 --> 00:33:43.390 align:middle line:84%
I used to play that on
the piano hours on end.

00:33:43.390 --> 00:33:44.190 align:middle line:90%
GOLDSTEIN: Right.

00:33:44.190 --> 00:33:47.080 align:middle line:84%
