and imagine that you're

00:33:49.163 --> 00:33:50.380 align:middle line:90%
hearing "Greensleeves."

00:33:50.380 --> 00:33:51.880 align:middle line:90%
And that's what's amazing.

00:33:51.880 --> 00:33:55.090 align:middle line:84%
She was moving out of the state
and having those benefits.

00:33:55.090 --> 00:33:57.100 align:middle line:90%
